keyAttributes.Materials: Pine & miscellaneous wood mixed, no additives, environmentally friendly
keyAttributes.Packing: By ton bag 24 tons/container 40’HC; 25kg woven bag, 24 tons/container 40’HC; No packing 26 tons/container
